{"tid":2184064,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"郭明錤：華為可能退出手機市場  受美國制裁影響零件不足","createTime":"2020-09-01T10:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T06:11:34.000Z","uid":339805,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f56b0476071e5d6986cef7c3755c374f4b2ec1b3","tid":2184064,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:11:41.000Z","msg":"美國對中國的出口禁制持續不斷，而對為的相關制裁更是從未間斷，目前仍未確定是否能夠在 9 月 15 日後尚能取得手機零件，令外界估計華為或會因而退出手機市場。<br />\n <br />\n天風證券知名分析師郭明錤近日發表最新研究報告，無論華為能否成功取得供應鏈，其在手機市場的競爭力與市占率都將受負面影響，而其估計，最壞情況是華為將會退出手機市場，而 Apple 以及 Oppo、vivo 與小米等其他中國手機廠商，則有望在更大範圍內取得華為原有的市場占有率。<br />\n <br />\n不過，郭明錤補充，華為以往需求的零件產品規格都比較高，其對相機、HDI、記憶體與 5G 晶片的零組件規格與單價要求明顯高於 Android 其他競爭對手，故若其決定退出手機市場，相信仍會為依賴華為的零件供應商帶來衝擊，且相關零件技術升級趨勢將放緩。<br />\n <br />\n郭明錤強調，2021 年手機零件產業鏈將面臨更大壓價壓力，在規格升級趨勢放緩情況下，品牌只能對零件廠商壓價以抵消 5G 手機的上升成本。且因市場有共識將 2021 年 5G 手機滲透率由 15% 至 20%，大幅增至 35% 至 45%。故價格將會快速下調。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/31/huaweismartphone/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F31%2Fhuaweismartphone%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYYtKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=b310d684\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/31/huaweismartphone/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"d83a1fc3ce4d1d95caa583dcca8b0fbe6410d0d5","tid":2184064,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be660f4c9e33a5108e794d37cb5bdf061e50b10","tid":2184064,"uid":109780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:32:26.000Z","msg":"捱多幾個月等拜登上台咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a0qgOTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa0qgOTM.jpg&h=7782e2e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2530a6ed5f2b557f8e969fc582d63a690840bfe9","tid":2184064,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:32:27.000Z","msg":"d人只不過會轉去samsung同Asus<br />\n需求係到無左一間廠會去得邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce2ef653323c9f610b3fb2b395decdf9f758482","tid":2184064,"uid":257468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:34:47.000Z","msg":"小粉紅: 那就好，我可以安心用苹果不怕被批斗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48ffebec2bebe8494aae24dc3fdbfb73a5b934b","tid":2184064,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:34:53.000Z","msg":"都係會去番中資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5df4d994b4dbdcfa2603578c927397bf717c14","tid":2184064,"uid":157312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"幾時到小米佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家市佔頭6有4間都係支那廠"},{"pid":"ca19fdfc142bedc930e818dc86e86f1691f3b18d","tid":2184064,"uid":271398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37f627fc51ad85342ecb502c1529cb63829cea49","tid":2184064,"uid":271398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T06:11:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}